flowchart LR
    py[Python script] --> run[subprocess.run]
    run --> cmd[[external command]]
    cmd --> out[capture stdout/stderr<br/>+ return code]
    out --> chk{return code == 0?}
    chk -->|yes| ok[use output]
    chk -->|no| err[handle error]

    class py,run,out,ok,err app
    class cmd ext
    class chk edge
